data.name: label1.Text
data.value:
Enter the information you want to fill into the "Technician" field by default on launch. Note that this information can be changed later and does not have to be displayed on the finished labels.
This data should be in the format of intials in the scheme of "First. Middle. Last." If you wish to have more than one technician, separate by "/". Example: R.A.V. / K.R.S.

data.name: label4.Text
data.value:
Enter the information you want to fill into the "Purchase Order" field by default. Note that this information can be changed later and does not have to be displayed on the finished labels.
This data should be a copied over in its native format. Example: 10711
